{"tid":2022620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過 直接9月立法會投票日一齊癱瘓投票站","createTime":"2020-05-18T12:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T16:35:47.000Z","uid":302,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d96a093b5056b47f4ba14168782097f5073785ca","tid":2022620,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過我地再投票只會再一次進入體制輪迴度<br />\n<br />\n區選已經證明左一個事實 <br />\n<br />\n今日霸王硬上弓 再一次證明呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家想睇同一個畫面幾多次？<br />\n<br />\n投票呢個行動 根本就係一個老鼠賽跑既遊戲<br />\n<br />\n要攬炒 就應該由一開始就玉石俱焚  <br />\n<br />\n徹徹底底咁黎一次 置諸死地而後生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於投票日點樣癱瘓 暫且無須討論實際行動 <br />\n<br />\n仲有大把時間 我地既可以柔克剛 也可剛柔並濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但大家要先有呢個覺悟 清走舊有既mind set<br />\n<br />\n否則就算35+贏左 都只係再一次進入體制輪迴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎激烈討論"},{"pid":"535ebe9b47005894801ac781a32c99b5f67f2e82","tid":2022620,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"上一次區選 大家都有默契唔好搞票站 以免跌入林鄭圈套 唔知而家區選贏就贏左 大家肯覺醒未"},{"pid":"72e274b1bc93336d902a70a7a46a88d8185d3f9e","tid":2022620,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69daffe082d9349c735d5e138101b44938bb94f1","tid":2022620,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f4d28ae334eb69d0b19daedf44d4703da55320","tid":2022620,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"一年後再睇返呢個po <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀唔好意思 到時已經上唔到連登"},{"pid":"ca819db99ed262abc83aa07b3a5f52d61ebd510e","tid":2022620,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\